README

To regenerate the data from scratch:

 - download Wikipedia dumps (check wikipedia/README)

 - compile corpus and syllables (rustc -O ...)

 - run ./run.sh


SCRIPTS

bn = Bengali
hi = Hindi / Devanagari
ta = Tamil
or = Oriya
te = Telugu
gu = Gujarati
pa = Punjabi / Gurmukhi
ml = Malayalam
kn = Kannada
si = Sinhala

